subSubSection.paragraph:
Description.
Male (
holotype
). Habitus as in 
Figs 3-5
. Total body length 4.12 (excluding the chelicerae). Carapace 2.08 long, 1.62 wide, 0.80 high. Sternum 0.94 long, 0.66 wide. Eye sizes: AME 0.39, ALE 0.24, PME 0.07, PLE 0.21. General coloration black, with numerous light grey setae on pars cephalica, the mid area of pars thoracica and opisthosoma. Sternum, labium and maxillae the same colour as carapace, with whitening in the anterolateral sides of maxillae. Cheli- cerae dark reddish brown. Opisthosoma without any distinct pattern (
Figs 3-4
). Legs light yellowish brown, with darker patterns on femora (
Fig. 3
). Measurements of legs: I: 5.87 (1.55, 1.03, 1.55, 1.19, 0.55), II: 4.34 (1.24, 0.85, 0.99, 0.78, 0.48), III: 4.29 (1.25, 0.70, 0.95, 0.89, 0.50), IV: 4.45 (1.33, 0.67, 1.08, 0.89, 0.48). Spination of legs: I: Ti 2pl, 2rl, Mt 2pl, 2rl, II: Ti 2v, Mt 2pl, 2rl, III and IV: Ti 2v.
